import axios from 'axios'

import Problem from '@/components/Problem.vue'

export default {
  name: 'App',
    data(){
      return {
          problem_list:[]
      }
    },
    methods:{
      async getProblem(){
        let params = {}
        let data = (await axios.get('/api/problem/', {params})).data
        this.problem_list = data 
      }
    },
    components: {
      NavBar,
      Problem,
    }
}
